<plot>Old and bitter, Alvin just wants some peace and quiet in his last days. His wish, however, is not granted when a young, vibrant and ironically full of life Kevin becomes Alvin's hospice roommate. Through this "odd couple" relationship, Alvin learns that its not the minutes in our life, its the moments in your life that matter. This is a heartwarming, uplifting, and very funny story of living life to its fullest.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?456732</url></doc>
